body:
Scott Lang

So you guys have noticed that apart from the occasional “cap”, “widow”, and “big guy” the Avengers usually refer to one another by name when in battle?

But have you ever noticed that Scott Lang just… doesn’t?

He exclusively refers to Steve Rogers as “Captain America” (especially after that one slip-up with Hope).

He calls Clint Barton “Arrow Guy”.

Like, he knows their names (almost everyone does) but he still chooses to call most of them by either random names of their hero alter-egos.
